<!--
  Monochrome notification small-icon for the Sakinah app.

  Android requires notification small-icons to be a white silhouette on a
  transparent background. The launcher icon (full-colour Sakinah crescent)
  was incorrectly used here previously, which meant the system stripped
  colours and rendered an unrecognisable white square on the status bar.

  This drawable is a simple filled heart — matches the wellness theme,
  recognisable at 18-24dp, single-path so it scales cleanly.

  Coloured accent bar / circle on lockscreen is set via the channel's
  `colour` parameter in NotificationService.init().
-->
<vector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:width="24dp"
    android:height="24dp"
    android:viewportWidth="24"
    android:viewportHeight="24">
